.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET_STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-stats \- show entry count and balance for a wallet
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-stats
.I wallet_name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the number of ledger entries and net balance in satoshis.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
